Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在 再次见到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定又会撒娇的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而无法前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的多摩川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲夏的花依然开放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在707室等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还做了同样款式的浴衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再这样闲逛 我可要先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶 有蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又黑又大 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书上有写的 是很有名的蝴蝶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是黑凤蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑凤蝶？不是蝴蝶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫做黑凤蝶的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑凤蝶蝴蝶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟普通的蝴蝶有什么不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近和五月讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会让我想起以前的真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为那家伙只有六岁儿童的程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又说我什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要怎么系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:03:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要系和小八一样的蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是蝴蝶结 而是叫做花文库的腰带结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是年轻女孩子系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小八也不可以系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（厚脸皮哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是一年一度的多摩川烟花大会的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论大家多么忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这一天 一定会回到这间房子里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着同样的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可以了 就这点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天就开始喝酒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到放烟花就醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 每次见到泰都是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像是活化石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是隔了几个月时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会变啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 泰从高中开始就完全没变过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使活到一千岁 一定还是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸也没什么改变呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说身高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很罗嗦唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸 要不要冲个澡 换上浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是冲澡 我要沐浴 帮我放水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 遵命 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲呢 今天不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放烟花之前会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还是那么我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还穿着浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 伸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢这个古装人偶系列了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是给你买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快谢谢叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时光的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净化了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈合了内心的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也有无法愈合的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这间房子还是跟那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间在这里停住了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实伸他……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸夫怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚子浴 很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用这么担心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾也已经准备好了 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如今 我也有很多话想说给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在这间房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到的却尽是回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然屋里就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要乔装打扮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 八公呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是巧不准她来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他不是那种会为了看烟花这种小事罗嗦的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有联系就是没事的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不祥的证明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这次爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就成了真正的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无法停止流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为见面说清楚 就能够释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今才明白 在章司身边的那段时光才是最开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章司在成为我的恋人以前就已经是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要抛弃内心的芥蒂 仿佛就可以回到从前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而真的是永远失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就该好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（真）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在见到伸 也无法冷静地谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为寂寞 又会向他哭诉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有前科的人要自重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不想又一句话不说地背叛大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去的话 就应该说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jackson的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 快来吧 烟花已经开始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕见到伸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸夫他没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道 那家伙也很倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说不愿意走入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（的确如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（的确如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你不用在意他 赶快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真和泰也很期待见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么扫兴 现在才说不来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想快点见到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里 伸夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她都已经说不想见到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还留在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是说怕见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八果然还是很爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是你一厢情愿的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 我了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕见了面又会迷失的那种恐惧 我最了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和巧的婚礼是在两个星期以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在又和你旧情复燃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就真的陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当然会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就更不应该见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意和她一起陷入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你一直以来只是同情被前男友抛弃 又被巧玩弄的小八而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那根本不能算喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是喜欢她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你现在喜欢的是隔壁的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她和我有一样的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃药就无法工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此她还是很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从前就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢帮助陷入困境的女孩 就算她和自己完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是想充英雄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而一旦发觉自己有可能被牵连进去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸 她只是在挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是轻松的爱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜真是残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意这样做 想让他们陷入泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出那种话伸当然会认真起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八会比现在更痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸是和平主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他希望大家每天过着幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以努力想选择一条可以得到最好结果的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不认为避免争斗是一件轻松的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和自己的欲望抗争呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 要几份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算逞强 我也要让你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想快点见到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在跟你旧情复燃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八就会陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有看放烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次吃路边摊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是筷子很难用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会有提供叉子的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要宠坏他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然拉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假发会掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（小八）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经到了门口 但是没人开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非大家都先去看烟花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是房间里还亮着灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大家等不及就先出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才应该道歉 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪里看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到你们我再打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？女装？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不原意和她一起陷入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是轻松的爱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？真？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 大家都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌 真又学美里说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的钻石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼不请伸就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连我都不请呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰和真都请了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会唱朋克版的瓢虫桑巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？是什么样的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会买CD给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你重新编曲 用吉他演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸为了让你得到幸福 才选择退出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不幸福 他的牺牲就白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过巧的话 一定会让你哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你这么笨 爱上这种人 真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会因为他的一两次婚外恋就受不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以揍他揍到气消为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 河边挤满了人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有看到章司和他的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为一切都落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仿佛稍一侧目就会被冲散的人潮之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想拉住娜娜的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那与伸有着相同体温的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我若真的天真烂漫地拉住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让她觉得我反应迟钝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过指间的风 感觉格外地冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天早已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要努力工作咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜比任何人都期望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无法挽回的那个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜
